# Keep the Docker build context lean — the Nuxt.Dockerfile copies the whole
# monorepo so pnpm --frozen-lockfile sees the full workspace, but none of these
# need to ship into the build (they're regenerated or irrelevant at build time).
**/node_modules
**/.output
**/.nuxt
**/.turbo
**/dist
**/.data
.git
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store
compose/certs
docs/local-stack/screenshots
